OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain across northern
OL,7,FEngland will sink southwards this
OL,8,Fevening before fading. A few showers
OL,9,Fwill continue across the far north of
OL,10,FScotland and the far south of England.
OL,11,FDry elsewhere with clear spells.
OL,12,FFeeling chilly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FShowers in the southeast will
OL,15,Fease, but will continue across
OL,16,Fnorthern Scotland. Dry and bright
OL,17,Felsewhere with sunny spells. Windy in
OL,18,Fthe south and feeling cooler in places.
